-a124-46a7-9eac-6aaa8c4e8ce0","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["As with the rest of Amazon&#39;s Kindle devices, the Paperwhite comes with a default one-year warranty for hardware and software issues. You can get support for the Paperwhite through usual channels like phone agents, live chat, social media and an online support section on Amazon’s website. Available resources include documentation and frequently asked question sections."]},"id":"fcbc7fd4-ea2c-4901-8be1-505c9b3b07f0","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"fa23e9fb-7928-415e-829d-8dac22e6108b","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["With its established presence in the eBook market, Amazon&#39;s Kindle series remains the standard-bearer for eBook readers, and the Kindle Paperwhite upholds this standing. While the Paperwhite isn&#39;t without blind spots, like a lack of physical navigation buttons, the build quality and value make it a stellar option for users looking for a versatile eBook reader."]},"id":"a5b7390b-59d9-4280-95ae-4cf690be2486","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_50888","url":"/kindle-paperwhite-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-staff","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-staff","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Staff","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"EcXXb3s8QKwvex3rQshgX5","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-09-27T21:50:54Z","datePublished":"2010-09-27T21:50:54Z","name":"Kindle Paperwhite","synopsis":"Buyers looking for the best eBook reader often turn to Amazon's Kindle line. The Kindle family has a lot to offer any type of user: Entry-level users who need basic eReaders can spring for budget Kindles, while potential buyers with larger budgets can target Amazon's higher-end models.","review":{"rating":92,"verdict":"The Amazon Kindle Paperwhite has an excellent display and sturdy build quality. In addition to Amazon&#039;s